      ],
      "uncertainty": "None — the pattern is established and proven in multiple test files."
    },
    {
      "question_id": "q3",
      "answer": "TradeReceipt is an internal component defined inline within EventTradePanel.tsx (not exported). Testing its color-coding logic should be done through integration with the parent. When the mutation succeeds, the test should verify TradeReceipt renders with the correct values. Testing distinct impactScore thresholds (>0.5 danger, >0.2 warning, <=0.2 muted) with separate fixtures adds valuable coverage for risk-display behavior and is worth the 2-3 extra test cases. The impactColor logic uses inline style with CSS variables, so tests should check the rendered impact percentage text and optionally the style.color property on the impact element.",
